Package: nof1gen
Title: Analyzes N-Of-1 clinical trials
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Aris", "Paschalidis", email = "aris.paschalidis@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: http://github.com/arisp99/nof1gen
Description: A package for running analysis for N of 1 study trials. 
    Runs Bayesian linear regression, ordinal/logistic regression, and poisson regression.
    Includes different plots to visualize the results and raw data.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    coda (>= 0.19-2),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.1.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.6),
    MASS (>= 7.3-49),
    rjags (>= 4-8),
    scales (>= 1.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
